  "body": "<p>Guess what?! I partnered with <a href=\"https://t.fabfitfun.com/aff_c?offer_id=13&amp;aff_id=1939\">FabFitFun</a> on the amazing Ready, Set, Create! Art Kit, which is a Choice item in some <a href=\"https://t.fabfitfun.com/aff_c?offer_id=13&amp;aff_id=1939\">FabFitFun</a> Summer Boxes.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595581224878-3S915UDNMTMWTGTETPZG/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595581240797-PXMGDHX5B3S0RTUQHIVO/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I was so excited when <a href=\"https://t.fabfitfun.com/aff_c?offer_id=13&amp;aff_id=1939\">FabFitFun</a> asked me to help curate a kit and go into the development process of really making sure this art kit was great for everybody. We picked out really fun, bright colors for the acrylic paints and a canvas size that’s not too intimidating. The tools were really important to me so we picked my favorite size paint brush as well as the high quality round foam brush. </p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595581254950-1W72T93BOFSGS30N6DAF/6c-065A1223.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595581268650-OEEH42L2AQ9ZSFUO28ID/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I thought that these kits would be perfect for hosting your own art party with a bunch of friends, so I also shared some of my best art party tips <a href=\"https://fabfitfun.com/magazine/how-to-throw-art-party/\">over on the FabFitFun blog</a>!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595581289297-LW28640NMVF7WU55800B/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595581300858-OL0DJDSGDEH0PJ9XCTLO/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>This box is filled with $200+ worth of beauty, fashion, and lifestyle goodies that I know you’re going to love! Use the code AMYTANGERINE10 for $10 off your first box at <a href=\"https://t.fabfitfun.com/aff_c?offer_id=13&amp;aff_id=1939\">fabfitfun</a>!</p><p>Updated: Looks like they are working on the link that is indicated on the art kits. In the mean time, there are some videos showing different things you can do with your kit if you're a fabfitfun member, check them out <a href=\"https://fabfitfun.com/tv/summer-products\">here</a>. Thanks!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
